{
  "texts": [
    "Reciprocity rates were calculated for each network member of every network layer.",
    "The reciprocity ratio shows the proportion of mutual candidates.",
    "Using 1500 variables, we look for factors that are good predictors of belonging to positive (1) for leavers and neutral (0) for stayers classes.",
    "The aim of feature selection is to improve the prediction performance using data extraction, including preparing understandable data 35.",
    "The finding of fast and cost-effective predictors is also an objective of selection considering an objective function 36."
  ]
}